My Favourite Bathtime Gurgles was a twelve volume epic poem by Grunthos the Flatulent, whose life ended when his major intestine, in a desperate bid to save all life, jumped up his neck and throttled his brain just as he was about to give a reading of his poem.Excerpt
Relax mind.
Relax body.
Relax bowels.
Relax.
Do not fall over.
You are a cloud.
You are raining.
Do not rain.
While train.
Is standing at a station.
Move with the wind.
Apologise where necessary.Trivia
 In the television series, the poem was referred to as Zen And The Art Of Going To The Lavatory.
